Base graphics
========================================================
left: 55%
```{r, echo=FALSE}
library(datasets)
mtcars$am.f <- factor(mtcars$am,levels=c(0,1), labels=c("Automatic","Manual"))
mtcars$model <- rownames(mtcars)
```

```{r, eval=FALSE}
require(graphics)
attach(mtcars)
hist(disp,
     xlab="disp",
     col="orange",
     border="black",
     main="Histogram",
     cex.lab=1.5,
     cex.axis=1,
     cex.main=2)
```

