Lattice graphs
========================================================
left: 55%
```{r, eval=FALSE}
library(lattice)
barchart(
model~wt,
col="magenta",
border="red",
cex.names=0.7,
main=list("Barchart",
      cex=2),
xlab=list(label="wt",
      cex=1.5))
```

